1.0.name: wordpress/mylinksdump
1.0.description:
You can make link dump of favorite links you visit regularly.This plug-in can record number of visitors who click on each link. You can also have a bar called Branding bar on top of destination url to personalize and publicize your blog. on the other side there are some options that you can change to customize your link dump behaviour.If you prefer widget to display your link dump then you can activate myLinksDump widget.

You can add link to your links dump while you are surfing web using your browser. In order to do this, bookmark generated link(in setting pane) and press it when ever you see a good link. When you press this bookmark, you'll be presented with pop-up window filled with the URL and title of the link you've just saw. By the time you did this, you can type your remark on that link and press Add My Link! button.

Thanks to myLinksDump RSS output you can share your links with others and let them to put your links dump on their blogs or sites.

R
